ADDITIONAL TERMS:

This program uses OpenPGP encryption (openpgp.js) to provide end-to-end
encryption. The cryptographic functions are based on standard algorithms
(AES-256, RSA) and follow industry best practices for secure communication.

Users are responsible for:
- Securely managing their private keys
- Using strong passphrases for key protection
- Understanding the security implications of their configuration choices
- Keeping their software up-to-date with security patches

No warranty is provided for data loss, interception, or other security
failures. This software is provided "as is" without any guarantees.

